                     <interp inst="t17830910-2-person101" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , about the 30th of July, and produced me this power of attorney, he signed a receipt in the name of 
               <persName id="t17830910-2-person102">
                  George
                   Davis
               <interp inst="t17830910-2-person102" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830910-2-person102" type="given" value="George"></interp>
